  "chunks": [
    {
      "uid": "03733888-05cc-5975-9987-5b42be93befe",
      "clause_number": "preamble",
      "kind": "preamble",
      "page": 1,
      "paragraph_index": 1,
      "text": "CIRCULAR\nHO/38/12/11(5)2026-MIRSD-POD/I/14660/2026 June 24, 2026\nTo,\nAll registered Investment Advisers,\nInvestment Adviser Administration and Supervisory Body (IAASB)\nMadam/ Sir,\nSub: Ease of Doing Business – Relaxation in certification requirement for\nPersons Associated with Investment Advice (PAIA) – Sales and other non-\ncore services",
      "metadata": {
        "regulator": "SEBI",
        "source_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/sebi_data/attachdocs/jun-2026/1782299902147.pdf",
        "source_page_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/legal/circulars/jun-2026/ease-of-doing-business-relaxation-in-certification-requirement-for-persons-associated-with-investment-advice-paia-sales-and-other-non-core-services_102385.html",
        "raw_pdf_path": "../corpus/inbox/sebi/6dbc0f3c-1782299902147.pdf",
        "sha256": "6dbc0f3c6729b195216c1930df6d671f5b91809517a2a7afeffca3993d68d678",
        "downloaded_at": "2026-07-06T11:59:46Z"
      }
    },
    {
      "uid": "a22a5107-8af7-5843-898a-4da92a4946cd",
      "clause_number": "1",
      "kind": "numbered",
      "page": 1,
      "paragraph_index": 2,
      "text": "1. In terms of Regulation 7 of Securities and Exchange Board of India (Investment\nAdvisers) Regulations, 2013 (“IA Regulations”), Persons Associated with\nInvestment Advice (PAIA), shall, inter-alia, obtain relevant certification from\nNational Institute of Securities Market (NISM).",
      "metadata": {
        "regulator": "SEBI",
        "source_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/sebi_data/attachdocs/jun-2026/1782299902147.pdf",
        "source_page_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/legal/circulars/jun-2026/ease-of-doing-business-relaxation-in-certification-requirement-for-persons-associated-with-investment-advice-paia-sales-and-other-non-core-services_102385.html",
        "raw_pdf_path": "../corpus/inbox/sebi/6dbc0f3c-1782299902147.pdf",
        "sha256": "6dbc0f3c6729b195216c1930df6d671f5b91809517a2a7afeffca3993d68d678",
        "downloaded_at": "2026-07-06T11:59:46Z"
      }
    },
    {
      "uid": "3b883c99-ab9b-5de4-8d0c-9c0febf6cf6e",
      "clause_number": "2",
      "kind": "numbered",
      "page": 1,
      "paragraph_index": 3,
      "text": "2. Vide Gazette Notification dated January 02, 2025 under Securities and Exchange\nBoard of India (Certification of Associated Persons in the Securities Markets)\nRegulations, 2007, it was, inter-alia, specified that PAIA shall obtain certification\nfrom NISM by passing the “NISM Series-X-A: Investment Adviser (Level 1)\nCertification Examination” and the “NISM Series-X-B: Investment Adviser (Level 2)\nCertification Examination”.",
      "metadata": {
        "regulator": "SEBI",
        "source_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/sebi_data/attachdocs/jun-2026/1782299902147.pdf",
        "source_page_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/legal/circulars/jun-2026/ease-of-doing-business-relaxation-in-certification-requirement-for-persons-associated-with-investment-advice-paia-sales-and-other-non-core-services_102385.html",
        "raw_pdf_path": "../corpus/inbox/sebi/6dbc0f3c-1782299902147.pdf",
        "sha256": "6dbc0f3c6729b195216c1930df6d671f5b91809517a2a7afeffca3993d68d678",
        "downloaded_at": "2026-07-06T11:59:46Z"
      }
    },
    {
      "uid": "79ac7f2f-273f-5f3d-a054-15485f15ca29",
      "clause_number": "3",
      "kind": "numbered",
      "page": 1,
      "paragraph_index": 4,
      "text": "3. Based on the feedback from market participants and as a step towards ease of\ndoing business, it has been decided to specify a lighter NISM certification module\nfor PAIA, such as sales staff, relationship managers and other staff, who only\nperform sales and other non-core services. These staff have contact with the client\nbut are not directly associated or involved in investment advice related aspects.",
      "metadata": {
        "regulator": "SEBI",
        "source_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/sebi_data/attachdocs/jun-2026/1782299902147.pdf",
        "source_page_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/legal/circulars/jun-2026/ease-of-doing-business-relaxation-in-certification-requirement-for-persons-associated-with-investment-advice-paia-sales-and-other-non-core-services_102385.html",
        "raw_pdf_path": "../corpus/inbox/sebi/6dbc0f3c-1782299902147.pdf",
        "sha256": "6dbc0f3c6729b195216c1930df6d671f5b91809517a2a7afeffca3993d68d678",
        "downloaded_at": "2026-07-06T11:59:46Z"
      }
    },
    {
      "uid": "94109872-5b7e-5fc1-b8c6-e061af12d7f4",
      "clause_number": "4",
      "kind": "numbered",
      "page": 1,
      "paragraph_index": 5,
      "text": "4. Accordingly, the following is being specified:",
      "metadata": {
        "regulator": "SEBI",
        "source_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/sebi_data/attachdocs/jun-2026/1782299902147.pdf",
        "source_page_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/legal/circulars/jun-2026/ease-of-doing-business-relaxation-in-certification-requirement-for-persons-associated-with-investment-advice-paia-sales-and-other-non-core-services_102385.html",
        "raw_pdf_path": "../corpus/inbox/sebi/6dbc0f3c-1782299902147.pdf",
        "sha256": "6dbc0f3c6729b195216c1930df6d671f5b91809517a2a7afeffca3993d68d678",
        "downloaded_at": "2026-07-06T11:59:46Z"
      }
    },
    {
      "uid": "2e67fc11-f4df-5655-beef-456062f64766",
      "clause_number": "4.1",
      "kind": "numbered",
      "page": 1,
      "paragraph_index": 6,
      "text": "4.1. PAIA, who perform only sales and other non-core services, shall obtain\ncertification from NISM by passing the “NISM Series–XXV-B: Persons\nAssociated with Investment Advice (Sales and Other Non-Core Services)\nCertification Examination”, as mentioned in the NISM Communique No. NISM/\nCertification/ NISM-Series-XXV-B: Persons Associated with Investment\nAdvice (Sales and Other Non-Core Services) Certification Examination/ 2026/\n01 dated May 18, 2026.",
      "metadata": {
        "regulator": "SEBI",
        "source_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/sebi_data/attachdocs/jun-2026/1782299902147.pdf",
        "source_page_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/legal/circulars/jun-2026/ease-of-doing-business-relaxation-in-certification-requirement-for-persons-associated-with-investment-advice-paia-sales-and-other-non-core-services_102385.html",
        "raw_pdf_path": "../corpus/inbox/sebi/6dbc0f3c-1782299902147.pdf",
        "sha256": "6dbc0f3c6729b195216c1930df6d671f5b91809517a2a7afeffca3993d68d678",
        "downloaded_at": "2026-07-06T11:59:46Z"
      }
    },
    {
      "uid": "b247b372-af14-5e41-b3a0-48170e30d22b",
      "clause_number": "4.2",
      "kind": "numbered",
      "page": 2,
      "paragraph_index": 7,
      "text": "4.2. PAIA, other than those who perform sales and other non-core services, shall\ncontinue to obtain certification from NISM by passing the “NISM Series-X-A:\nInvestment Adviser (Level 1) Certification Examination” and the “NISM Series-\nX-B: Investment Adviser (Level 2) Certification Examination”.",
      "metadata": {
        "regulator": "SEBI",
        "source_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/sebi_data/attachdocs/jun-2026/1782299902147.pdf",
        "source_page_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/legal/circulars/jun-2026/ease-of-doing-business-relaxation-in-certification-requirement-for-persons-associated-with-investment-advice-paia-sales-and-other-non-core-services_102385.html",
        "raw_pdf_path": "../corpus/inbox/sebi/6dbc0f3c-1782299902147.pdf",
        "sha256": "6dbc0f3c6729b195216c1930df6d671f5b91809517a2a7afeffca3993d68d678",
        "downloaded_at": "2026-07-06T11:59:46Z"
      }
    },
    {
      "uid": "91463f46-ca02-5cde-a70e-ba7f0b868fd2",
      "clause_number": "5",
      "kind": "numbered",
      "page": 2,
      "paragraph_index": 8,
      "text": "5. The PAIA (as referred at paragraph 4.1 above) who have already obtained the\nNISM Series-X-A and NISM Series-X-B certifications, as on the date of this circular,\nshall not be required to undertake the NISM Series-XXV-B certification at this\nstage. Such PAIA shall obtain NISM Series-XXV-B certification only before expiry\nof the validity of their existing certifications.",
      "metadata": {
        "regulator": "SEBI",
        "source_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/sebi_data/attachdocs/jun-2026/1782299902147.pdf",
        "source_page_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/legal/circulars/jun-2026/ease-of-doing-business-relaxation-in-certification-requirement-for-persons-associated-with-investment-advice-paia-sales-and-other-non-core-services_102385.html",
        "raw_pdf_path": "../corpus/inbox/sebi/6dbc0f3c-1782299902147.pdf",
        "sha256": "6dbc0f3c6729b195216c1930df6d671f5b91809517a2a7afeffca3993d68d678",
        "downloaded_at": "2026-07-06T11:59:46Z"
      }
    },
    {
      "uid": "89153b88-a2c6-5949-bcdc-0e4ec8a726d7",
      "clause_number": "6",
      "kind": "numbered",
      "page": 2,
      "paragraph_index": 9,
      "text": "6. The provisions of this circular shall come into force with immediate effect.",
      "metadata": {
        "regulator": "SEBI",
        "source_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/sebi_data/attachdocs/jun-2026/1782299902147.pdf",
        "source_page_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/legal/circulars/jun-2026/ease-of-doing-business-relaxation-in-certification-requirement-for-persons-associated-with-investment-advice-paia-sales-and-other-non-core-services_102385.html",
        "raw_pdf_path": "../corpus/inbox/sebi/6dbc0f3c-1782299902147.pdf",
        "sha256": "6dbc0f3c6729b195216c1930df6d671f5b91809517a2a7afeffca3993d68d678",
        "downloaded_at": "2026-07-06T11:59:46Z"
      }
    },
    {
      "uid": "982f0430-650e-5b21-b14a-0a0507003b9a",
      "clause_number": "7",
      "kind": "numbered",
      "page": 2,
      "paragraph_index": 10,
      "text": "7. The Investment Adviser Administration and Supervisory Body, is advised to:\n7.1. make necessary amendments to the relevant bye-laws and rules, for the\nimplementation of this circular; and\n7.2. bring the provisions of this circular to the notice of the registered Investment\nAdvisers and also disseminate the same on its website.",
      "metadata": {
        "regulator": "SEBI",
        "source_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/sebi_data/attachdocs/jun-2026/1782299902147.pdf",
        "source_page_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/legal/circulars/jun-2026/ease-of-doing-business-relaxation-in-certification-requirement-for-persons-associated-with-investment-advice-paia-sales-and-other-non-core-services_102385.html",
        "raw_pdf_path": "../corpus/inbox/sebi/6dbc0f3c-1782299902147.pdf",
        "sha256": "6dbc0f3c6729b195216c1930df6d671f5b91809517a2a7afeffca3993d68d678",
        "downloaded_at": "2026-07-06T11:59:46Z"
      }
    },
    {
      "uid": "f5215e67-c798-5ca5-8f6d-54675b351947",
      "clause_number": "8",
      "kind": "numbered",
      "page": 2,
      "paragraph_index": 11,
      "text": "8. This circular is issued in exercise of powers conferred under Section 11(1) of the\nSecurities and Exchange Board of India Act, 1992, read with Regulation 7 of the\nSecurities and Exchange Board of India (Investment Advisers) Regulations, 2013\nand Regulation 3(1) of SEBI (Certification of Associated Persons in the Securities\nMarkets) Regulations, 2007, to protect the interests of investors in securities and\nto promote the development of, and to regulate the securities markets.",
      "metadata": {
        "regulator": "SEBI",
        "source_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/sebi_data/attachdocs/jun-2026/1782299902147.pdf",
        "source_page_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/legal/circulars/jun-2026/ease-of-doing-business-relaxation-in-certification-requirement-for-persons-associated-with-investment-advice-paia-sales-and-other-non-core-services_102385.html",
        "raw_pdf_path": "../corpus/inbox/sebi/6dbc0f3c-1782299902147.pdf",
        "sha256": "6dbc0f3c6729b195216c1930df6d671f5b91809517a2a7afeffca3993d68d678",
        "downloaded_at": "2026-07-06T11:59:46Z"
      }
    },
    {
      "uid": "eb44047f-1150-5593-bc03-3037d07fbaeb",
      "clause_number": "9",
      "kind": "numbered",
      "page": 2,
      "paragraph_index": 12,
      "text": "9. This circular is issued with the approval of the competent authority.",
      "metadata": {
        "regulator": "SEBI",
